Class ListSequence<T extends FeatureInput>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParamsInitializer<SharedFeaturesInitParams>, Provider<FeatureList<T>>

    public class ListSequence<T extends FeatureInput>
extends ReferencedFeatures<T>
    Populates a FeatureListElem with references to other features formed by one or two sequences of integers, so that all the features of the following pattern are contained in the list.

    prependString seperator sequenceInteger prependString seperator sequenceInteger seperator sequenceAdditionalInteger

    where all these are concatenated together.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
